headline: GTA Online
subtitle: FREAK OUT
content:
Under the LS Highway, there’s a new kind of hangout in town. Welcome to The Freakshop, your drug-fueled, no-holds-barred, Fooligan-friendly hideout, where there’s everything you need to keep you entertained.

For the serious: weapon upgrades and a vehicle workshop for Acid Labs and delivery bikes. For everyone else: beers and bongs. So sit down, take off your pants, and load up. Things are about to get weird.
